      step4Title: "Step 4: Create New Project",
      step4Desc: "As a buyer, create a new project by filling in project information such as project name, project number, project manager, and project type. This step allows you to organize and structure your construction project from the start.",
      step4DetailTitle: "Step 4: Create New Project",
      step4DetailIntro: "Create a new project to organize and structure your construction project. Follow the step-by-step instructions below to set up project information, assign project managers, and configure project settings.",
      step4DetailStep1Title: "Step 1: Access Project Creation",
      step4DetailStep1Text: "First, you need to log in to your account. Once logged in, click on your avatar at the bottom of the screen - a menu will appear where you can select 'Dashboard'. In the Dashboard, you will see the 'Projects' tab. Click on the 'Projects' tab, and then select 'New Project' to open the project creation window.",
